<div class="design-criteria">
  <div class="center-display">
    {{#link-to "design.index" class="bounce-up"}}
      <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-up"></i>
    {{/link-to}}
    <h2>Criteria</h2>
    <ul class="lead text-left">
      <li>
        The image processing algorithm must reliably differentiate between forks, knives, and spoons.
      </li>
      <li>
        Based on feedback from the image processing algorithms, the Zumy should navigate to the appropriate location.
      </li>
      <li>
        The Zumy should be able to move the utensil without losing it.
      </li>
      <li>
        The Zumy should avoid all obstacles on the field, and leave any existing utensil piles undisturbed.
      </li>
      <li>
        On a request, the dispenser must dispense one random utensil in a configuration suitable for Zumy pickup.
      </li>
      <li>
        Once the dispenser is empty (i.e. the task is finished), the Zumy should disengage.
      </li>
    </ul>
    {{#link-to "design.choices" class="bounce-down"}}
      <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"></i>
    {{/link-to}}
  </div>
</div>